again with you.

23:56.026 --> 23:59.296
- Very soon.
- I think we should talk now.

23:59.796 --> 24:01.131
Goodbye.

24:01.231 --> 24:05.201
- Oh, come on. This is ridic...
- Goodbye. For now.

24:05.301 --> 24:07.136
Come on.

24:07.403 --> 24:10.139
Yeah, okay. See ya around.

25:08.697 --> 25:10.566
Celebration time?

25:11.100 --> 25:12.569
